WEBVTT

00:00.720 --> 00:01.440
In reply to Father

00:01.760 --> 00:02.760
Your son and that Yu Gong

00:02.880 --> 00:03.720
Do not know each other

00:03.960 --> 00:04.840
Your son only heard of this

00:05.000 --> 00:06.240
This morning

00:06.520 --> 00:07.480
Is that so?

00:07.840 --> 00:10.120
A subject deceiving his sovereign loses his head

00:10.480 --> 00:11.600
A son deceiving his father

00:11.960 --> 00:12.880
What should be done?

00:14.960 --> 00:16.720
This is the Imperial City Guard's report

00:16.840 --> 00:17.840
Read it yourself

00:28.840 --> 00:29.480
Your son is wronged

00:29.760 --> 00:30.840
This report from the Imperial City Guard

00:31.320 --> 00:32.440
Your son truly cannot understand

00:33.120 --> 00:34.840
Your son has never been anyone's patron

00:35.360 --> 00:36.360
Wronged or not

00:36.720 --> 00:38.360
You know in your heart

00:39.360 --> 00:40.520
Just imprisoning your elder brother

00:40.720 --> 00:41.440
Your mother

00:41.440 --> 00:43.360
Has been ill for days
